.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, indie, r&b, classical, dubstep
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, baseball, cricket, badminton, water-polo
5 different games are played: bridge, poker, snooker, mah-jongg, go
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, van, bus, boat, helicopter

1. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of reggae
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person driving the tram
3. the person drinking coffee is the fan of indie
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking tea
5. the fan of indie is to the right of the fan of r&b
6. the person playing bridge is the person driving the helicopter
7. the person playing poker is the fan of classical
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left
10. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person driving the van
11. the person playing poker is to the left or right of the person driving the boat
12. the person playing mah-jongg is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person playing go
14. the person who's sport is badminton is to the left or right of the fan of dubstep

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Sport	|   badminton	|    cricket	|     handball	|    baseball	|    water-polo	|
| Music-Genre		|    classical	|      dubstep	|      reggae	|     r&b	|     indie	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Game		|     poker	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| mah-jongg	|   parliament	|
| Transport		|     van	|     boat	|     helicopter	|     tram	|     bus	|
